---
import IndexLayout from "../layouts/IndexLayout.astro";
---
<IndexLayout>
	<section class="rounded-md grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 mt-9 md:gap-20 md:grid-cols-2 bg-white p-12">
		<div>
			<h1 class="text-center font-bold text-xl mb-8 md:text-left">DNM-Itools</h1>
		<p class="mb-2 text-center md:text-left md:mb-4">解決您四面八方問題的金鑰</p>
		<p class="mb-2 md:mb-4">我們提供專業領域相關的基礎知識，給予更簡便的工具，滿足您的各方需求</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
			<a href="#" class="border rounded-md bg-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[280px]">
				<span class="block text-center">精選文章</span>
				<button  class="bg-white block text-center mt-24 border rounded-md p-1">More</button>
				</a>
				<a href="#" class="border rounded-md bg-gray-200 p-4 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[280px]">
					<span class="block text-center">精選文章</span>
					<button  class="bg-white block text-center mt-24 border rounded-md p-1">More</button>
					</a>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="rounded-md bg-white mt-6 p-6 md:p-12">
		<h2 class="text-center font-bold text-xl mb-8 md:text-left">線上工具，安心服用</h2>
	</section>
	<section class="rounded-md bg-white mt-6 p-6 md:p-12">
		<h2 class="text-center font-bold text-xl mb-8 md:text-left">知識文章分享</h2>
	</section>
	<section class="rounded-md bg-white mt-6 p-6 md:p-12">
		<h2 class="text-center font-bold text-xl mb-8 md:text-left">Contact us</h2>
		<p class="mb-6 text-center md:text-left">如果對於工具有任何想優化，或者是希望網站上新增什麼樣的簡易工具，都歡迎與我們聯繫，感謝各位的支持。</p>
		<div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
			<a href="#" class="bg-bg border rounded-md p-2">立即聯繫</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</IndexLayout>
